# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/

# Generated by Tauri
# will have schema files for capabilities auto-completion
/gen/schemas

# Machine-local Cargo config. Currently holds a rust-lld linker override that
# speeds up incremental dev relinks on Windows. Kept untracked on purpose: the
# benefit is local-only, and committing a linker override would impose it on CI
# and the Windows release build (which don't benefit and shouldn't bear the
# risk). Each machine can opt in with its own copy.
/.cargo/
